snippet.title: THE HIBERWORLD APP IS HERE 📱
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD NOW: https://hiberworld.onelink.me/JOv8/legkq143

Be part of the Hiber community on the go with the new HiberWorld App! It is now available to download on the App store for iOS in 166 countries! ✨

Browse and play 3D experiences of all kinds, connect with friends, and create your own experiences straight in the app! 😍

#HiberWorldApp #NewHiber #HiberWorld

Stay Connected:
►Discord: https://discord.gg/sXK4TyR
►Twitter: https://twitter.com/hiberworld
►TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@hiberofficial
►Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hiberofficial/

If you enjoyed this content please subscribe and like this video!
